'''''The Lucasfilm Fan Club Magazine'' 3''' is the third issue of [[Star Wars Insider|''The Lucasfilm Fan Club Magazine'']], later rebranded as the ''Star Wars Insider''. Issue 3 was published in Spring [[1988]].

{{Magazine-stub|issue}}

==Contents==
===Features===
*"The Magic of ''Willow'' Premieres May, 1988" by [[Dan Madsen]]
*"Val Kilmer: Introducing Madmartigan" by Dan Madsen & [[John S. Davis]]
*"[[Mark Hamill: 10 Years Later]]" {{C|by Dan Madsen}}
*"The Car Is the Star: A Close-Up Look at the Tucker Automobile" by [[Lisa E. Cowan]]

===Departments===
*"The Fan Forum"

